eath.  See also  Margery  ,   Marjorie ."],"variants":[{"name":"Margareta","meanings":["From the Latin form of Greek <i>Margarītēs</i>.  See  <b>Margaret</b>   ."]},{"name":"Margaretta","meanings":["Formed from Margaret."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Margaret was born about 0988, in Normandy, France. She had at least 1 son with Viscount, Roger de Berkeley I Vicount of Berkeley."},"et":{"about 0988–Deceased":"umbes 0988–Surnud","0987–Male":"0987–Surnud","1012–1042":"1012–1042","0988–Female":"0988–Surnud","about 0988":"umbes 0988","1012":"1012","1042":"1042","0987":"0987","0988":"0988","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 0988–Deceased":"noin 0988–Kuollut","0987–Male":"0987–Kuollut","1012–1042":"1012–1042","0988–Female":"0988–Kuollut","about 0988":"noin 0988","1012":"1012","1042":"1042","0987":"0987","0988":"0988","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Ranska"},"fr":{"about 0988–Deceased":"environ 0988–Décédée","0987–Male":"0987–Décédé","1012–1042":"1012–1042","0988–Female":"0988–Décédée","about 0988":"environ 0988","1012":"1012","1042":"1042","0987":"0987","0988":"0988","Normandy, France":"Normandie, France","lifeSummary":"Margaret est née environ 0988, à Normandie, France. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Viscount, Roger de Berkeley I Vicount of Berkeley."},"de":{"about 0988–Deceased":"um 0988–Verstorben","0987–Male":"0987–Verstorben","1012–1042":"1012–1042","0988–Female":"0988–Verstorben","about 0988":"um 0988","1012":"1012","1042":"1042","0987":"0987","0988":"0988","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Margaret wurde um 0988 in Normandie, Frankreich geboren. Sie hatte mit Viscount, Roger de Berkeley I Vicount of Berkeley mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"about 0988–Deceased":"about 0988–Desede","0987–Male":"0987–Desede","1012–1042":"1012–1042","0988–Female":"0988–Desede","about 0988":"about 0988","1012":"1012","1042":"1042","0987":"0987","0988":"0988","Normandy, France":"Normandie, France"},"hu":{"about 0988–Deceased":"0988 körül–elhunyt","0987–Mal